719
00:27:23,729 --> 00:27:25,600
Um... but it's Jason,
my husband.

720
00:27:25,644 --> 00:27:27,994
That's what I wanted
to talk to you about.

721
00:27:28,037 --> 00:27:29,169
Oh.

