your own instincts.

794
00:30:34,223 --> 00:30:36,835
I have to tell you, though,
if you open this door

795
00:30:36,878 --> 00:30:38,924
you have to be prepared
to walk through it.

796
00:30:38,967 --> 00:30:40,099
Mm-hmm.

797
00:30:43,189 --> 00:30:47,149
Oh, I just want everything to be
like it was in the beginning.

798
00:30:47,193 --> 00:30:51,762
I really don't know
if I could survive without him.

799
00:30:51,806 --> 00:30:55,070
Then maybe you should think
about this a little more.

800
00:30:55,114 --> 00:30:56,550
Hmm.

